Scott Pilgrim vs. the World;;84;;82;;PG-13;;As bass guitarist for a garage-rock band, Scott Pilgrim (Michael Cera) has never had trouble getting a girlfriend; usually, the problem is getting rid of them. But when Ramona Flowers (Mary Elizabeth Winstead) skates into his heart, he finds she has the most troublesome baggage of all: an army of ex-boyfriends who will stop at nothing to eliminate him from her list of suitors.;;Romance,Action,Comedy;;Edgar Wright;;2010;;Michael Cera,Mary Elizabeth Winstead,Kieran Culkin,Chris Evans,Anna Kendrick,Brie Larson,Alison Pill,Aubrey Plaza,Brandon Routh,Jason Schwartzman,Johnny Simmons,Mark Webber,Mae Whitman,Ellen Wong,Shôta Saitô,Satya Bhabha,Keita Saito;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/scott_pilgrims_vs_the_world